Problem definition
==================

Users want a GUI to transcode movies.


Design choices
==============

This tool is written in C and follows the GNOME guidelines.


Authors
=======

Alexandre Quessy <alexandre@quessy.net>


Dependencies
============

GLib, GTK+, ffmpeg.


License
=======

GPL v3.


See also
========

Basic usage of MEncoder: http://www.mplayerhq.hu/DOCS/HTML/en/mencoder.html
Video and Audio file format conversion: http://www.ffmpeg.org/ffmpeg-doc.html#SEC18
http://en.gentoo-wiki.com/wiki/HOWTO_Mencoder_Introduction_Guide

